{"tid":1909663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有權用盡]青年辱國旗判社服令　律政司申請加刑改判監禁","createTime":"2020-03-04T06:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:10:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2505efef02dec48b6e7c81c88b2b4f7e64f77f13","tid":1909663,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"去年9月有市民在沙田新城市廣場集會，21歲冷氣技工學徒涉踐踏國旗、將國旗丟進垃圾車和水池等，遭警方拘捕。他早前在裁判法院承認一項侮辱國旗罪，被判200小時社會服務令。律政司今（4日）申請覆核刑期，認為原審裁判官未有考慮罪行嚴重性、被告加刑因素等，建議改判監禁。上訴庭聽畢雙方陳辭後，宣布押後頒判辭。<br />\n<br />\n羅敏聰（21歲）早前承認去年9月22日在沙田新城市廣場及大會堂一帶，公開及故意以毁損、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗。原審裁判官當時考慮到被告認罪和沒案底，加上行為不涉焚毁國旗，判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200304/s00001/1583300706432/%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e8%be%b1%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%97%e5%88%a4%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%8d%e4%bb%a4-%e5%be%8b%e6%94%bf%e5%8f%b8%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e5%8a%a0%e5%88%91%e6%94%b9%e5%88%a4%e7%9b%a3%e7%a6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200304%2Fs00001%2F1583300706432%2F%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25be%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2597%25e5%2588%25a4%25e7%25a4%25be%25e6%259c%258d%25e4%25bb%25a4-%25e5%25be%258b%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258f%25b8%25e7%2594%25b3%25e8%25ab%258b%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%2594%25b9%25e5%2588%25a4%25e7%259b%25a3%25e7%25a6%2581&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a214c3fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200304%2Fs00001%2F1583300706432%2F%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25be%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2597%25e5%2588%25a4%25e7%25a4%25be%25e6%259c%258d%25e4%25bb%25a4-%25e5%25be%258b%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258f%25b8%25e7%2594%25b3%25e8%25ab%258b%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%2594%25b9%25e5%2588%25a4%25e7%259b%25a3%25e7%25a6%2581&h=9a69384a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/