ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"503de5c2c75d61f9053ccda4daae85cce3ebea14","tid":1909663,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"嚴重性響邊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc33ab21f00044c5ade1951d37801059decb93a","tid":1909663,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDiDAfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDiDAfq.png&h=fcbf32b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AY7H1Vr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAY7H1Vr.png&h=1ebcf7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ruptly/status/1146923902234320898?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fruptly%2Fstatus%2F1146923902234320898%3Fs%3D21&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=facb77a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fruptly%2Fstatus%2F1146923902234320898%3Fs%3D21&h=f2afbdea\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ruptly/status/1146923902234320898?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"a0d89f15d6f9785bf778079ef26320109373fc2f","tid":1909663,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"有啲連登仔話咩野啲錢唔好拎來打官司 直接俾手足屋企人<br />\n<br />\n我睇到真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯 有啲罪可能斷正 點都入到<br />\n<br />\n但法庭唔係只判有無罪嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n同樣傷人 襲警 個律師會用不同以往嘅案例爭辯似邊單多啲<br />\n<br />\n律政司一定會用重個單案例 辯方就用輕個單<br />\n<br />\n唔俾錢打官司嘅下場就變左只能用啲好差嘅當值律師 俾律政司吊起身撚<br />\n<br />\n手足屋企人的確會多左生活費<br />\n<br />\n但手足就由原本坐3-4年變左坐6-7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0278964bbc56c3ee84346a3393845043ba6950","tid":1909663,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"侮辱支那國旗係最直接非暴力政治犯罪<br />\n<br />\n如果政府堅持判監，<br />\n如果手足拒捕並走入美國領事館<br />\n希望美國會庇護佢"}]}